<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{قَالَ اخْرُجْ مِنْهَا مَذْءُومًا مَدْحُورًا}</span> يَعْنِي: مَذْمُومًا مُبْعَدًا}.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُحَمَّدٌ:</span> تَقُولُ: ذَأَمْتَ الرَّجُلَ؛ إِذَا بِالَغْتَ فِي عَيبه وذمه.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سُورَة الْأَعْرَاف من الْآيَة <span class="c2">(١٩)</span> إِلَى الْآيَة <span class="c2">(٢٥)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>